  "style_summary_en": "Second-generation sushiya led by Chef Junya Kudo.\nUtilizes only specific fishing and slaughter methods, aging fish up to one month.\nExercises rigorous ingredient control—personally boarding fishing vessels since his Hokkaido days to verify quality.\nAwarded Tabelog Gold BEST NEW ENTRY in 2024.",
  "style_summary_jp": "シェフ工藤淳也による2世代目の鮨屋。\n特定の漁獲・処理方法のみを使用し、最長1ヶ月の熟成。\n北海道時代から漁船に直接乗船して食材を検証するほどの強い食材管理。\n2024年Tabelog Gold BEST NEW ENTRY受賞。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Sushi for connoisseurs, defined by chef mastery and ingredient depth.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "強いシェフ統制と食材の深みで魅せるマニア領域の鮨。"
